 und Zielen im Einklang steht."}, "en": {"title": "Advanced Materials Revolutionizing Building Envelope Applications", "summary": "Advanced materials are emerging as a transformative force in the construction industry, particularly in building envelope applications. Sources like Deloitte Insights and the Advanced Material Market Size report highlight the growing market potential and innovations in materials that enhance energy efficiency and structural performance. This matters for the building-envelope industry because optimizing materials can lead to safer, more durable, and environmentally friendly structures, aligning with sustainability goals and regulatory standards.", "rationale": "The driving force behind the trend is technological, as advanced materials are specifically highlighted as transformative innovations enhancing energy efficiency and structural performance in building envelope applications. The evidence from reports like Deloitte Insights emphasizes the market potential and innovations in this area. Environmental considerations are also relevant, as the focus on sustainability aligns with regulatory standards and goals."}}	\N
