also carried out to verify its behavior under cyclic loading and understanding its ability to counteract the actions of the wind and earthquake.	https://openalex.org/W2903113965	2018-11-30 00:00:00	en	\N	\N	\N	2026-06-08 13:54:21.908253	\N	\N	\N	\N	\N	\N	f
